'''梅蘭妮·譚蒂維·「譚蒂」·紐頓·帕克'''，[[英帝國官佐勳章|OBE]]（'''Melanie Thandiwe "Thandie" Newton Parker'''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.downingcambridge.com/famous-downing-college-alumni |title=Famous Downing College Alumni - Downing College |publisher=Downingcambridge.com |date=2015-08-25 |accessdate=2016-07-18 |archive-date=2016-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828023725/http://www.downingcambridge.com/famous-downing-college-alumni |dead-url=no }}</ref>，{{bd|1972年|11月6日|||Newton, Thandie}}），[[英國|英國]][[女演員|女演員]]<ref name="Times070908">Graydon, Nicola; [http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article4666651.ece "Thandie Newton on becoming Condoleezza Rice"] {{Wayback|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article4666651.ece |date=20110615075159 }} ''The Times'' (London), 7 September 2008</ref><ref name="Trib210908">Carty, Ciaran; [http://www.tribune.ie/archive/article/2008/sep/21/when-thandie-met-condi/ "When Thandie met Condi"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tribune.ie/archive/article/2008/sep/21/when-thandie-met-condi/ |date=20100122203849 }} ''Tribune.ie'', 21 September 2008</ref> 。她常現身於多部賣座[[英國|英國]]和[[美國電影|美國電影]]，代表的有《[[當幸福來敲門|當幸福來敲門]]》、《[[求愛馬拉松|求愛馬拉松]]》、《[[不可能的任務2|不可能的任務2]]》、《[[衝擊效應|衝擊效應]]》和[[小布希|小布希]]傳《[[殊不簡單|殊不簡單]]》。

==早期生活==
譚蒂·紐頓生於[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]，母親是[[辛巴威|辛巴威]]醫療工作者，父親尼克·紐頓<ref>Barton, Laura; [http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2008/may/28/water.usa "'I was so incredibly self-conscious'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2008/may/28/water.usa |date=20081211083935 }} ''Guardian.co.uk'', 28 May 2008</ref>是[[英國|英國]]實驗工程師。<ref name="Ind311008">Lewis, Sian; [http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/thandie-newton-condi-was-my-hardest-role-ever-979864.html "Thandie Newton: 'Condi was my hardest role ever'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/thandie-newton-condi-was-my-hardest-role-ever-979864.html |date=20090607100450 }} ''Independent.co.uk'', 31 October 2008</ref>她的出生地常被誤報為[[非洲|非洲]][[尚比亞|尚比亞]]<ref name="Yah!M">[http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800018708/bio "Thandie Newton Biography"] {{Wayback|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800018708/bio |date=20060409103416 }} ''Yahoo! Movies''</ref>，然而在訪談中已證實她出生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]，在她雙親旅行兩週的期間。<ref name="KamW-240308">Williams, Kam; [http://www.kamwilliams.com/2008/03/thandie-newton-run-fatboy-run-interview.html "Sweet as Thandie"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kamwilliams.com/2008/03/thandie-newton-run-fatboy-run-interview.html |date=20080720144105 }} ''KamWilliams.com'', 24 March 2008</ref><ref name="NewsBlaze">Williams, Kam; [http://newsblaze.com/story/20080324113427tsop.nb/topstory.html "Sweet as Thandie"] {{Wayback|url=http://newsblaze.com/story/20080324113427tsop.nb/topstory.html |date=20100122113928 }} ''NewsBlaze.com'', 24 March 2008</ref><ref name="BBC-040608">''A Taste of My Life'', Series 4 (BBC Two, 4 June 2008) Thandie Newton — Quote: "Nigel Slater (host): ''You were born in London but you didn't stay here for long did you? You went down to Cornwall?'' Thandie Newton (answers): ''Actually I don't know how my mum and dad managed to do this. But we lived in Zambia, and my mum was pregnant with me. And I was born on a two-week trip back to London, and then we went back to Zambia and my brother was born there. And we ended up coming to England finally when I was three years old. So my dad could help out with the family antique business.''"</ref>「譚蒂維（{{small|Thandiwe}}）」在部分[[非洲|非洲]]民族語言意指「摯愛的（{{small|beloved}}）」<ref>[http://www.thinkbabynames.com/meaning/1/Thandiwe "Thandiwe — name meaning and origin"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thinkbabynames.com/meaning/1/Thandiwe |date=20090620084235 }} ''ThinkBabyNames.com''</ref>，發音念法為「Tan-dee」。<ref name="IMDbiog">[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0628601/bio "Biography for Thandie Newton"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0628601/bio |date=20081220195607 }} ''IMDb.com''</ref>根據紐頓說法，她的母親是名辛巴威紹納族的公主。<ref name="Teleg-051006">Sullivan, Chris; [http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3645552/Why-Newton-favours-gravity-over-fluff.html "Why Newton favours gravity over fluff"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3645552/Why-Newton-favours-gravity-over-fluff.html |date=20100124143143 }} ''Telegraph.co.uk'', 5 October 2006</ref> 
成長於[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]和[[康沃爾|康沃爾]]，1992年至1995年就讀於[[劍橋大學唐寧學院|劍橋大學唐寧學院]]的[[社會人類學|社會人類學]]系，以中等成績畢業。<ref name="DowCam">[http://www.dow.cam.ac.uk/dow_server/news/Thandie.html "News and Events: Downing alumna Thandie Newton wins BAFTA award"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dow.cam.ac.uk/dow_server/news/Thandie.html |date=20100122191300 }} ''Dow.Cam.ac.uk''</ref>

